title: Mortal Kombat Legacy II Abridged
description:
This is all ten episodes merged together without all the Machinima splatter.
Each episode is merged seamless as possible. I actually cut the second episode short because we see the whole Kenshi fight twice. So what I did was have the main intro start right when Kenshi and Ermac clash, then on to Kitana Mileena story where they watch the fight with you rather than, again, with you.
I croped 125 pix from top and bottom to remove WS bars with Machinima logo. File format is still the same as original. My first time editing an HD mp4, I think it went well!
My upload is capped at 1MBs so ill keep seedin for at least a week if not more. Enjoy, Mortal Kombat.
